@startuml UC09_Sequence
title UC09: 录入成绩 - 顺序图

actor "教师" as Teacher
boundary "成绩录入界面" as EntryForm
control "成绩控制类" as GradeCtrl
entity "Grade" as Grade

Teacher -> EntryForm : 选择课程并录入学生分数
EntryForm -> GradeCtrl : saveGrades(studentScores)
loop 为每个学生
    GradeCtrl -> Grade : createOrUpdate(sid, cid, scores)
    Grade --> GradeCtrl : success
end
GradeCtrl --> EntryForm : 返回计算后的总评及保存成功提示
EntryForm -> Teacher : 显示录入成功
@enduml
